<title>About -ZppixBot</title>
<h1>About</h1>
<body>
ZppixBot is an IRC bot running <a href="https://sopel.chat">Sopel</a> 6.5.1 and Python 2.7.9. The current release of ZppixBot customizations is version 3.0. ZppixBot has lots of commands and more can be added by writing more modules. The home channel for ZppixBot is <a href="irc://chat.freenode.net/#ZppixBot">#ZppixBot</a> where you can get help from the maintainers. ZppixBot's current maintainers are MacFan4000, Zppix and Reception123.</body>